text: Lisa Carlsen (born 17 February 1965) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1987 Pan American Games Category:Equestrians at the 2019 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Toronto
